<header class="topbar"><div><div class="eyebrow">Live controls</div><h1>Runtime controls</h1><p class="subtitle">Changes are persisted in SQLite, audited, and applied immediately without a redeploy.</p></div></header>
{{#if notice}}<div class="notice">{{notice}}</div>{{/if}}
<section class="grid two-col">
  <article class="card"><div class="card-head"><div><h2>Generation and quota policy</h2><p>Environment values remain the fallback defaults.</p></div></div><div class="card-body"><form method="post" action="/admin/settings"><input type="hidden" name="csrf_token" value="{{csrfToken}}"><div class="switch-row"><div><strong>Accept new speech generations</strong><div class="hint">When paused, cached audio remains available but uncached requests receive HTTP 503.</div></div><input type="checkbox" name="generation_enabled" {{#if settings.generationEnabled}}checked{{/if}}></div><div class="form-grid" style="margin-top:16px"><div class="field"><label for="daily_character_quota">Daily character quota</label><input id="daily_character_quota" name="daily_character_quota" type="number" min="1" max="100000000" value="{{settings.dailyCharacterQuota}}" required><div class="hint">Per installation. Environment default: {{number defaults.dailyCharacterQuota}}.</div></div><div class="field"><label for="daily_generation_quota">Daily generation quota</label><input id="daily_generation_quota" name="daily_generation_quota" type="number" min="1" max="1000000" value="{{settings.dailyGenerationQuota}}" required><div class="hint">Per installation. Environment default: {{number defaults.dailyGenerationQuota}}.</div></div><div class="field"><label for="max_chunk_characters">Maximum chunk length</label><input id="max_chunk_characters" name="max_chunk_characters" type="number" min="100" max="50000" value="{{settings.maxChunkCharacters}}" required><div class="hint">Environment default: {{number defaults.maxChunkCharacters}} characters.</div></div><div class="field"><label for="log_retention_days">Log retention</label><input id="log_retention_days" name="log_retention_days" type="number" min="1" max="365" value="{{settings.logRetentionDays}}" required><div class="hint">Request traces and events older than this are pruned.</div></div></div><div class="form-actions"><button class="primary" type="submit">Save runtime settings</button></div></form></div></article>
  <aside class="grid"><article class="card"><div class="card-head"><div><h2>Retention maintenance</h2><p>Run the active retention policy now.</p></div></div><div class="card-body"><p class="muted" style="font-size:12px;line-height:1.6;margin-top:0">Normal pruning runs periodically as traffic arrives. This control immediately removes request and event records older than {{settings.logRetentionDays}} days.</p><form method="post" action="/admin/logs/prune"><input type="hidden" name="csrf_token" value="{{csrfToken}}"><button type="submit">Prune expired logs now</button></form></div></article><article class="card"><div class="card-head"><div><h2>Environment-owned settings</h2></div></div><div class="card-body"><p class="muted" style="font-size:12px;line-height:1.7;margin:0">Admin credentials, provider API keys, signing secrets, model identity, public URL and network limits stay deployment-managed. Update them in Dokploy and redeploy; they are intentionally not editable here.</p></div></article></aside>
</section>
